Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%labels
AUTHOR Clean-up Exercise Prep
DESCRIPTION Container prepared for the “component metadata clean-up” task.

%post
    set -e

    # Install Python and pytest
    apt-get update
    DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        python3 \
        python3-pip
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Prepare the initial project directory and input TSV files expected
    # by the learner’s task and by the autograder’s *initial-state* tests.
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    mkdir -p /home/user/project

    cat > /home/user/project/component_a.tsv <<'EOF'
comp_login	v1.2	alice
comp_payments	v2.0	bob
comp_notifications	v1.4	carol
comp_search	v1.8	dave
EOF

    cat > /home/user/project/component_b.tsv <<'EOF'
comp_login	stable
comp_payments	deprecated
comp_notifications	beta
comp_search	stable
EOF

    # Ensure the agent (non-root runtime user) can read/write in the project dir
    chmod -R a+rwX /home/user/project

%help
    chmod 755 /home/user

This image provides the starting state for the “component metadata clean-up”
exercise:

  • /home/user/project/component_a.tsv   (3 columns)
  • /home/user/project/component_b.tsv   (2 columns)

Python 3 and pytest are installed for automated grading.